    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior is clean with only minor surface scratches and small stone chips from normal driving. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronics functioning as intended. It drives smoothly and represents a solid, reliable choice for its next owner.",
